</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Apple M1 Ultra 晶片發布，詳細規格 + 20 核心處理器</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/09/new-m1-ultra-chip/notebook/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=new-m1-ultra-chip</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[高威]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 08 Mar 2022 19:32:09 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[桌上電腦]]></category><category><![CDATA[流動電腦]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[M1 Ultra]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1089723</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>2022 年 Apple 首個發布會，沒有發布傳聞中的 M2 晶片，反而是在 M1 系列上增加最高階的一款晶片 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>2022 年 Apple 首個發布會，沒有發布傳聞中的 M2 晶片，反而是在 M1 系列上增加最高階的一款晶片 M1 Ultra。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.32.06-AM.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089727" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.32.06-AM-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.32.06-AM-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.32.06-AM-1280x719.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.32.06-AM-768x431.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.32.06-AM-1536x863.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.32.06-AM-2048x1150.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.32.06-AM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>基本規格</h2><p>M1 Ultra<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span>是由兩顆 M1 Max 以其 UltraFusion 的特別封裝架構，連接兩塊 M1 Max 所組成。此款晶片將會用在全新推出的 Mac Studio 上。M1 Ultra 使用 5nm 製程，內含高達 1140 億個電晶體，而兩顆處理器之間的頻寛可達 2.5TB/s。Mac 電腦會將其認作一顆晶片，因此現行軟件皆可通用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.34-AM.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089733" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.34-AM-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.34-AM-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.34-AM-1280x719.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.34-AM-768x431.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.34-AM-1536x863.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.34-AM-2048x1150.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.34-AM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.28.52-AM.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089736" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.28.52-AM-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.28.52-AM-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.28.52-AM-1280x719.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.28.52-AM-768x431.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.28.52-AM-1536x863.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.28.52-AM-2048x1150.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.28.52-AM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a h