href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.07-AM.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089732" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.07-AM-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.07-AM-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.07-AM-1280x719.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.07-AM-768x431.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.07-AM-1536x863.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.07-AM-2048x1150.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.29.07-AM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>M1 Ultra 擁有 20 核心 CPU，其中 16 個為高效能核心，4 個節能核心；支援最高 64 核心的 GPU，運算能力高達 21 Teraflops；另外配備 32 核心的神經網絡引擎。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.31-AM.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089737" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.31-AM-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.31-AM-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.31-AM-1280x719.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.31-AM-768x431.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.31-AM-1536x863.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.31-AM-2048x1150.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.31-AM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.23-AM.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089738" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.23-AM-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.23-AM-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.23-AM-1280x719.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.23-AM-768x431.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.23-AM-1536x863.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.23-AM-2048x1150.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.23-AM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.47-AM.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089741" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.47-AM-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.47-AM-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.47-AM-1280x719.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.47-AM-768x431.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.47-AM-1536x863.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.47-AM-2048x1150.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.47-AM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> </a></p><p>記憶體方面，M1 Ultra 最高支援 128GB 統一記憶體，記憶體頻寛可 800GB/s。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.10-AM.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089731" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.10-AM-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.10-AM-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.10-AM-1280x719.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.10-AM-768x431.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.10-AM-1536x863.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.10-AM-2048x1150.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.10-AM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>效能比較</h2><p>Apple 在發布會上亦指 M1 Ultra 的能源效益更好，比起其自家的 M1 晶片快 8 倍。在同樣的能源消耗下，M1 Ultra 的 CPU 比起現有的 16 核心 CPU 電腦節省 90% 能源；而 GPU 比起現時最高階的獨立顯示核心節省 200W 的能源。</p><p>另外，M1 Ultra 在 Mac Studio 上可以播放多達 18 段 8K ProRes 422 的影片串流。</p><p>M1 Ultra 將會在新登場的 Mac Studio 可選配。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.34-AM-1.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089743" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.34-AM-1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.34-AM-1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.34-AM-1-1280x719.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.34-AM-1-768x431.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.34-AM-1-1536x863.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.34-AM-1-2048x1150.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.30.34-AM-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.27-AM.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089744" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.27-AM-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.27-AM-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.27-AM-1280x719.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.27-AM-768x431.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.27-AM-1536x863.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.27-AM-2048x1150.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.27-AM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.53-AM.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089745" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.53-AM-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.53-AM-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.53-AM-1280x719.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.53-AM-768x431.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.53-AM-1536x863.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.53-AM-2048x1150.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Screenshot-2022-03-09-at-2.31.53-AM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
