</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>iPhone 13 / iPhone 13 Pro 松嶺綠色，香港價錢 + 發售日期</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/09/iphone-13-iphone-13-pro-green-new-colour/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=iphone-13-iphone-13-pro-green-new-colour</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Edward]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 08 Mar 2022 18:45:38 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[手提電話]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone 13]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone 13 mini]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone 13 Pro]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone 13 Pro Max]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1089696</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>去年 Apple 推出了全新的 iPhone 13 中階旗艦系列及 iPhone 13 Pro 旗艦系列，引來 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>去年 Apple 推出了全新的 iPhone 13 中階旗艦系列及 iPhone 13 Pro 旗艦系列，引來不少用家搶購，但相信大家對 iPhone 11 Pro 系列的軍綠色念念不忘。今日凌晨 Apple 舉行的春季發佈會，就宣佈推出全新的軍綠色版本的 iPhone 13 Pro 系列，亦將此軍綠色引入到中階旗艦系列 iPhone 13 上，令大家在新機上，都可以用回吸引的軍綠色設計。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-family-lineup-220308.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089698" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-family-lineup-220308-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-family-lineup-220308-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-family-lineup-220308-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-family-lineup-220308-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-family-lineup-220308-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-family-lineup-220308-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-family-lineup-220308.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>全新的綠色版 iPhone 13 及松嶺綠色版 iPhone 13 Pro 將會在本星期五，亦即是 3 月 11 日正式接受預訂，並會在 3 月 18 日正式發售。定價方面，iPhone 13 mini 及 13 將會是 $5,999 及 $6,799 起，而 iPhone 13 Pro 及 13 Pro Max 將會是 $8,499 及 $9,399 起。容量方面，iPhone 13 mini 及 iPhone 13 將會提供 128GB、256GB 及 512GB 3 個選擇，而 iPhone 13 Pro 及 13 Pro Max 則會提供 128GB、256GB、512GB 及 1TB 4 個選擇，而 4 部 iPhone 本身擁有的顏色，仍會繼續發售。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-Pro-color-lineup-220308.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089699" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-Pro-color-lineup-220308-694x496.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="496" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-Pro-color-lineup-220308-694x496.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-Pro-color-lineup-220308-1260x900.jpg 1260w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-Pro-color-lineup-220308-768x549.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-Pro-color-lineup-220308-1536x1097.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-Pro-color-lineup-220308.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-color-lineup-220308.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089700" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-color-lineup-220308-694x496.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="496" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-color-lineup-220308-694x496.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-color-lineup-220308-1260x900.jpg 1260w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-color-lineup-220308-768x549.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-color-lineup-220308-1536x1097.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Apple-iPhone13-color-lineup-220308.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
